{"tid":1747652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇大埔保皇班撚樣嘅黑材料？","createTime":"2019-11-23T10:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T12:38:19.000Z","uid":102646,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b8260cd17b919fc9c10adc5358f2018991259e","tid":1747652,"uid":102646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:18:04.000Z","msg":"屋企班廢老廢中成日覺得保皇好人全部正人君子嚟，想搵下有冇佢地嘅黑材料，等全世界都知佢地啲仆街事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔建制派侯選人<br />\n<br />\n大埔墟 張國慧<br />\n頌汀 譚榮勳<br />\n大埔中 梅少峰<br />\n大元 鄭俊平 蘇馬俊<br />\n富亨 胡綽謙<br />\n怡富 羅志平<br />\n富明新 吳卓穎<br />\n廣福及寶湖 黃碧嬌<br />\n宏福 胡健民<br />\n大埔滘 陳笑權<br />\n運頭塘 余志榮<br />\n新富 羅曉楓<br />\n林村谷 陳灶良<br />\n寶雅 葉俊傑<br />\n太和 鄭俊和<br />\n舊墟及太湖 劉文杰<br />\n康樂園 鄧銘泰<br />\n船灣 劉志成<br />\n西貢北 李華光<br />\n<br />\n利申：住廣福但係係就放喺全部建制撚樣上嚟"},{"pid":"39e737eb04307848525639ee2be807f7a58e0e44","tid":1747652,"uid":102646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"自推下先 1/10"},{"pid":"6913d7eb70728c367e706a8ef92d4436b11fd2fa","tid":1747652,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"官商勾結"},{"pid":"20d96df3c4d10ba52f9e1c87969adf1648d1d561","tid":1747652,"uid":325346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"防暴強行進入富雅花園、羅曉楓自稱訓左要半夜先到場處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3eacfd84480f993130ddc65c5c065d78978bbb","tid":1747652,"uid":102646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:21:23.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"604a7ec11e3d77f80a08fb3ee0feb50546f35f3f","tid":1747652,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"張國慧明明是民建聯扮獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa